title: Sweet House

container.value:
145 Hennessy Road, Wan Chai
18/F On Hong Commercial Building

creator: MAFT Wireless
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the Sweet House! This is a mansion that belongs to you, you can decorate it into your favorite style! Here you can realize your design dreams, use your design talents to decorate your dream house, homescapes, gardenscapes, resort and so on, more scenes are waiting for you to open!

Although the mansion is huge, don't worry, your assistant, housekeeper and maid will help you with the home makeover and home restoration! You can also raise a cute kitten in the villa, play with it, communicate with the neighbors... Here you can experience interesting mansion story and story garden, it will make you more interesting while playing! This is a brand new design home game, come and join us!

House Design Gmaes:

- A variety of gameplay methods, let you experience unprecedented gaming fun!

-Different plots have different pass requirements, complete it in a limited number of steps. Come and meet the challenge!

-Dress yourself and your pet, wear the latest clothes, and buy cute clothes for your beloved pet!

-You can choose the style you like for all the decorations and furniture！

-Get star rewards after passing the levels, explore more new areas！

-Interesting and fascinating plots！

Sweet House is a puzzle matching game, very suitable as a family game, play home design game with your friends on Facebook, there are also rich stand-alone game modes, you can experience the fun of the game without internet connection!

If you have any questions or suggestions in the game, please contact us via Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/Sweety-House-1897449780302861
We will hold events from time to time through FB, and there are rich rewards and benefits, don't miss it!
